# AI tooling
docs/superpowers/

# typedoc output is regenerated fresh by CI on every run via
# `pnpm --filter @miden-sdk/miden-sdk run typedoc`. Don't commit the
# tree — the "Check that web client documentation is up-to-date" step
# in test.yml runs `git diff --exit-code` over this path, which is a
# no-op when the dir is untracked. Treat the step as a warning-only
# smoke test; the canonical API reference is the typedoc output
# rendered on the published docs site.
docs/typedoc/
